PeopleBot

D. Campion
G. Fabre

Slack Bot used to send queries to https://people.total database.

Authentication on the people.total api is done using OAuth v2.0 protocol.
https://oauth.net/2/

Note:
The basis of the bot is built on the following tutorial:
https://www.fullstackpython.com/blog/build-first-slack-bot-python.html

How to set up PeopleBot:
1 - Setup Slack api
2 - Create setting.xml
3 - pip install slackclient
5 - enjoy
